Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and learned about the ruler of the island - Caesar Clown's motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All while trying to escape Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,along with their pirate ally - the Warlord - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and the others are on the move to kidnap Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-- save the children, and escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--No! --Give it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give us the candy already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, spit them all out! Mocha, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you what kind of drug they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! I-I don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Caesar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.85,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Brownbeard in Grief! Luffy Lands a Furious Blow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinokuni, the deadly gas, is flowing into the Third Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and starting to fill up B Building where the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the Navy G-5, and the children are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not this way! Go back, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only gas - how is it outpacing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you went the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep still, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedate them already, G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A few more to go, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't resist, children! --Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up, raccoon dog! We don't have time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t give up, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo... Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait, Kin'emon-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go that way, you'll run into the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even see any soldiers, let alone my people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that creepy room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was captured by Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--He looks okay. --Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Video Transponder Snail is running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers of Punk Hazard! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're watching me somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all being fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar is telling you nothing but lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all gonna die if you stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he gone crazy after being captured by the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard is on the floor below - R Building 1st floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Straw Hats and Navy soldiers will arrive there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,soon according to your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we tell Brownbeard to come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the truth about Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming with you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my dear underling - Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you got away from Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You look awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Why are you in such a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my people back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We got robbed at the center of the island but they didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, he's messing with the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Your people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be one of Brownbeard's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! There are Navy soldiers at the main entrance and it's closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get inside! Please guide us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! That's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see what I can do! Wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, how are you going to let them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinokuni will be inescapable out there soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even call me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're not here, they must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried? I think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were out there, they're definitely dead because of Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing, Brownbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust your words anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--What happened to him?! --What is he doing to the Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you guys this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because we spent the last two years together on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the island now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna know what he called you behind your back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This was his special name for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Guinoa pags.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Guinoo pah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guinoa poh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Guinoh... Guinah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you trying to say, Brownbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Speak clearly! --Is it some kind of spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Guinoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They will keep following me thinking I'm their savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know that I kept them alive because they're my guinea pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Guinea pigs"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! I got tongue-tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You did something, didn't you, Caesar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you putting on an act?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you okay? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a muscle relaxant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing strength around your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and your whole body, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember now, Brownbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,About your former subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I let them die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you kill my people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is another thing that I'd like to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The chemical weapon explosion that nearly killed all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,these soldiers four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who caused it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This bastard did harm to everybody and pretended that he saved them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Brownbeard is going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's been going on this island is all staged by Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, guys! He's a devil disguised as a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do that to a person who saved you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! He's really dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Straw Hat did something to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Shoot him! He's gonna attack you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let me finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastane...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we make it out of that hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You climbed that wall to the top, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let me finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It grazed my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His kindness saved my life as it did to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master was our warm-hearted savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to 2nd floor, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats and the Navy will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--Get ready for the experiment! --Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Broadcast it for the brokers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's go! --Hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume they'll all be dead in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So we need to find more kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one who were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...harming those kindhearted children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,People on this island were tricked into being here, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything so let me tell you the secret of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--There's no sound! --Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--Checking the video! --Pull the elevator up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is like gas or air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An island that doesn't seem to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, this island shouldn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's suitable to the work of an underground community.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an epicenter of evil science.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do unlawful experiments or get test subjects illegally as we like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some powerful people backing us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll cover up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So no one out there would know a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you cry or scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,no one will come to the rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know a damn thing about this island, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're getting involved without taking it seriously, you'll end up dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Allying with Law is also not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to mess with SAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He is using you to kidnap me because I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the only person who can create SAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you about SAD, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The most dangerous Warlord - Don Quixote Doflamingo owns this factory
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and here, SAD is processed into a fruit called "SMILE."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what SMILE is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We successfully recreated a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,SMILE is a Zoan type, man-made Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who wants to become powerful yearns for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo is selling SMILEs to big-timers in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard one of the Four Emperors is already on the move...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...to form an army of hundreds of Devil Fruit users with SMILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it send a chill down your spine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what you're dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By interfering with Doflamingo's business, you'll piss so many big names off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When they start going into action, it's gonna shake up the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what Law wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're out of your league!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can! But I'm protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo! The Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even have balls to pick a fight with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna run, do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...picking fights all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Undaunted by the powerful Gas Gas Fruit attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luffy corners Caesar with his fists of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But elsewhere, Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,facing another powerful Haki user,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is fighting an overwhelmingly losing battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and lies on the verge of death and defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Surprising Outcome! Ashen Hunter vs. Vergo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
